  "name": "Restful Pause",
  "type": "spell",
  "effects": [],
  "system": {
    "description": {
      "gm": "",
      "value": "<h4 dir=\"ltr\">Restful Pause SPELL 1</h4>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">[Uncommon][Transmutation][Dynamic Heightening]</p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Traditions </strong>primal</p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Access </strong>earth-bound</p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Cast </strong>[two-actions] somatic, verbal</p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Range </strong>Touch</p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Duration </strong>1 minute</p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\"> </p>\n<hr />\n<p> </p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">With a touch, the target feels a powerful compulsion to lay down. The target is not forced to do so, but if they do, they gain fast healing 1 for the duration of the spell. If the target stands up from prone after laying down, the spell ends for them. If the target receives the full duration of healing, they may make fresh saving throws against any afflictions they are suffering, which cannot worsen the condition.</p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\"> </p>\n<hr />\n<p> </p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Heightened (+1)</strong> The fast healing is increased by 3.</p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Heightened (+1)</strong> One additional target may be affected within range and the range of the spell increases to 30 feet.</p>\n<p><strong>Heightened (+1)</strong> The target(s) does not need to be prone, but must avoid strenuous activity (such as using more than one action a round)</p>"
    },
